*[[Special attack]] weapon such as a [[dragon dagger]]. If using the [[Arkan blade]] as a main-hand damaging weapon, its special attack will suffice.
*[[Divine super combat potion]]s / [[super combat potion]]s; or [[super attack potion]]s + [[super strength potion]]s if those are not available.
*Means to teleport to house, such as [[Teleport to house (tablet)]] or [[Construction cape]]
*[[Rune pouch]], with runes to cast [[Resurrection spells]] and a [[Book of the dead]].
**If [[A Kingdom Divided]] has not yet been completed, simply bring [[nature rune]]s and [[fire rune]]s for [[High Level Alchemy]].
*[[Explorer's ring 4]] if high alching runite item drops and using the [[Arceuus Spellbook]].
*[[Herb sack]] if collecting herb drops.
*[[Bonecrusher]] or [[bonecrusher necklace]] for Prayer experience and to reduce number of items on ground.
*A [[bracelet of slaughter]] to switch to as the boss dies, if wishing to prolong Slayer task.
* Some food to heal from occasional off-prayer attacks or mistakes. If no longer getting hit by special attacks in the fight, cheaper food may be brought.

High-level players may forgo food by using the [[Saradomin godsword]]'s special attack to heal, but should keep in mind that it unequips the player's shield as well, possibly lowering their total weight. Low-level players may use a knife on the [[watermelon]] drops to eat [[watermelon slice]]s, or bring a [[tinderbox]] and filled [[log basket]] or [[axe]] to cook the raw food drops outside of the cave.
