{{Incomplete|Quick preliminary equipment recommendations based on dps calcs, could probably use improvements and additions. Needs DPS calc on venge vs thralls.}}
Due to Shellbane gryphon's cave's proximity to fairy ring {{Fairycode|CJQ}}, players who have [[ornate rejuvenation pool]] and [[Fairy ring (Construction)|fairy ring]] built in their [[player-owned house]] can teleport out between kills and restore their [[hitpoints]], [[Special attacks|special attack]], and [[prayer points]]. This has three major benefits:
* Less supplies used
* Allows special attacks to be used more often
* Allows player to bring better equipment
** The weight aspect of gryphon's knockback can be ignored, since it's unlikely that the gryphon will do that more than once per kill and the damage taken is only moderate. 
~50-65 kills per hour can be achieved with this method, depending on what gear player has access to, and how attentively they are playing.

